   FACIL'iti - Paramétrage
   Your site + easy access

Adapt website display to fit your habitual or temporary needs

   I want to know what FACIL'iti can do for me

   FACIL'iti adapts websites according to your needs and navigation
   comfort

   FACIL'iti provides a solution for those who have difficulty seeing and
   for who have motor disabilities or incomplete comprehension.

   Just create a customized profile online; FACIL'iti takes care of the
   rest.

   Websites equipped with FACIL'iti will automatically adapt to your
   profile. It's quick, easy and free of charge.
   Logo FACIL'iti

   To operate, FACIL'iti must create a cookie. This cookie is used only to
   activate the solution. It does not collect data on your browsing
   pathway and will not transmit information to any partners. By
   continuing to browse on this site and by using FACIL'iti, you authorize
   creation of this cookie.
